Class GridComputerEdge

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.gridgraph.structure.GridElement

  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public class GridComputerEdge
extends GridEdge
    A wrapper class for GridEdge instances inside graph computing environment. Specifically, operations that are valid on edge in computing environment are implemented here.
